co.cask.cdap.api.procedure
Interface ProcedureResponder

Deprecated. As of version 2.6.0, replaced by HttpServiceResponder 

@Deprecated
public interface ProcedureResponder

This interface defines a response generator. Caller should either call stream(ProcedureResponse) to stream data back to client or call sendJson(ProcedureResponse, Object) to send json object back to client.

stream

ProcedureResponse.Writer stream(ProcedureResponse response)
                                throws IOException
Deprecated. 
Adds the response to be returned to the caller. Calling this method multiple times to the same ProcedureResponder will return the same ProcedureResponse.Writer instance and any newer ProcedureResponse will be ignored.

Parameters:
response - A ProcedureResponse containing the response to be returned.
Returns:
An instance of ProcedureResponse.Writer for writing data of the response.
Throws:
IOException - When there is an issue sending the response to the callee.
